TITLE: Displaying Druid Configuration Directory Structure
DESCRIPTION: Shows the recommended organization of Druid configuration files across different service directories and components.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/druid-website/blob/asf-site/docs/0.14.1-incubating/configuration/index.md#2025-04-09_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
$ ls -R conf
druid       tranquility

conf/druid:
_common       broker        coordinator   historical    middleManager overlord

conf/druid/_common:
common.runtime.properties log4j2.xml

conf/druid/broker:
jvm.config         runtime.properties

conf/druid/coordinator:
jvm.config         runtime.properties

