TITLE: Executing SQL TopN Query in Apache Druid
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows an SQL query equivalent to the native JSON TopN query. It retrieves the top 10 Wikipedia pages with the most edits on 2015-09-12 using Druid SQL syntax.
