TITLE: Configuring Log4j2 for Apache Druid
DESCRIPTION: This XML snippet demonstrates a sample log4j2.xml configuration file for Apache Druid. It sets up console logging with a specific pattern layout and configures the root logger level to 'info'. It also includes a commented-out section for enabling logging of all HTTP requests.
