TITLE: Configuring Parquet Parser with TimeAndDims ParseSpec in Druid
DESCRIPTION: JSON configuration example for ingesting Parquet files using the 'parquet' parser with a 'timeAndDims' parseSpec. This approach specifies dimensions explicitly without using field discovery or flattening.
