TITLE: Using Selector Filter with Extraction Function in Apache Druid
DESCRIPTION: This example shows a selector filter combined with a lookup extraction function to match transformed dimension values. It filters for products that map to 'bar_1' in the lookup table.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/druid-website/blob/asf-site/docs/0.15.1-incubating/querying/filters.md#2025-04-09_snippet_19

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
    "filter": {
        "type": "selector",
        "dimension": "product",
        "value": "bar_1",
        "extractionFn": {
