TITLE: Constructing a Search Query in Apache Druid
DESCRIPTION: This JSON snippet demonstrates how to structure a search query in Apache Druid. It includes essential parameters such as queryType, dataSource, granularity, searchDimensions, query specification, sort order, and time intervals.
