TITLE: Constructing a Timeseries Query in Druid
DESCRIPTION: A complete example of a timeseries query in Druid showing the main query components including queryType, dataSource, granularity, filters, aggregations, postAggregations, and intervals. This query retrieves daily aggregated data with specified filters and calculations.
