TITLE: Configuring Segment Storage for Historical in YAML
DESCRIPTION: YAML configuration for segment storage in Historical processes, including cache locations and deletion settings.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/druid-website/blob/asf-site/docs/0.15.1-incubating/configuration/index.md#2025-04-09_snippet_38

LANGUAGE: yaml
CODE:
```
druid.segmentCache.locations:
  - path: "/mnt/druidSegments"
    maxSize: 10000
    freeSpacePercent: 1.0
druid.segmentCache.deleteOnRemove: true
druid.segmentCache.dropSegmentDelayMillis: 30000
druid.segmentCache.infoDir: ${first_location}/info_dir
druid.segmentCache.announceIntervalMillis: 5000
druid.segmentCache.numLoadingThreads: ${Number of cores}
druid.coordinator.loadqueuepeon.curator.numCallbackThreads: 2
```

