SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/druid-website/blob/asf-site/docs/0.15.0-incubating/querying/aggregations.md#2025-04-09_snippet_16

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "type" : "stringFirst",
  "name" : <output_name>,
  "fieldName" : <metric_name>,
  "maxStringBytes" : <integer> # (optional, defaults to 1024),
  "filterNullValues" : <boolean> # (optional, defaults to false)
}
```

