TITLE: Executing a View Query in Apache Druid
DESCRIPTION: This JSON snippet shows how to structure a view query in Apache Druid. It includes the query type 'view' and a nested groupBy query, demonstrating how to leverage materialized views for query optimization.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/druid-website/blob/asf-site/docs/0.15.1-incubating/development/extensions-contrib/materialized-view.md#2025-04-09_snippet_1

