SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/druid-website/blob/asf-site/docs/0.14.2-incubating/ingestion/schema-changes.md#2025-04-09_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: text
CODE:
```
foo_2015-01-01/2015-01-02_v2_0
foo_2015-01-01/2015-01-02_v2_1
foo_2015-01-01/2015-01-02_v2_2
```

