TITLE: Configuring Avro Stream Parser with Schema Repo
DESCRIPTION: Example configuration for setting up an Avro stream parser using schema repository for data ingestion. Includes schema repo decoder configuration with subject and ID converter settings.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/druid-website/blob/asf-site/docs/0.14.0-incubating/development/extensions-core/avro.md#2025-04-09_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "parser" : {
    "type" : "avro_stream",
    "avroBytesDecoder" : {
      "type" : "schema_repo",
      "subjectAndIdConverter" : {
        "type" : "avro_1124",
        "topic" : "${YOUR_TOPIC}"
      },
      "schemaRepository" : {
        "type" : "avro_1124_rest_client",
        "url" : "${YOUR_SCHEMA_REPO_END_POINT}"
      }
    },
    "parseSpec" : {
      "format": "avro",
      "timestampSpec": <standard timestampSpec>,
      "dimensionsSpec": <standard dimensionsSpec>,
      "flattenSpec": <optional>
    }
  }
}
```

