TITLE: Configuring Kafka 0.8.x Firehose in JSON for Apache Druid
DESCRIPTION: Sample JSON configuration for setting up a Kafka 0.8.x firehose in Apache Druid. This configuration establishes connection to Zookeeper, sets consumer group properties, and specifies the Kafka topic to ingest data from.
