TITLE: Implementing Kafka Producer for Protobuf Messages
DESCRIPTION: Python script that reads JSON data, converts it to Protobuf format, and publishes it to a Kafka topic.
SOURCE: https://github.com/apache/druid-website/blob/asf-site/docs/0.14.1-incubating/development/extensions-core/protobuf.md#2025-04-09_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: python
CODE:
```
#!/usr/bin/env python

import sys
import json

from kafka import KafkaProducer
from metrics_pb2 import Metrics

producer = KafkaProducer(bootstrap_servers='localhost:9092')
topic = 'metrics_pb'
metrics = Metrics()

for row in iter(sys.stdin):
    d = json.loads(row)
    for k, v in d.items():
        setattr(metrics, k, v)
    pb = metrics.SerializeToString()
    producer.send(topic, pb)
```

