TITLE: Configuring and Running insert-segment-to-db Tool with MySQL and S3
DESCRIPTION: This example shows how to run the insert-segment-to-db tool with MySQL as metadata storage and S3 as deep storage. It includes the necessary Java VM arguments, S3 configuration, and command-line options.
